<td style="text-align: center;">
<p style="text-align: left; padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #183661;"><span style="font-size: large;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><span style="text-shadow: #ffffff 0px 1px 1px;"><span style="font-size: medium;"><strong><span style="color: #126daf;">இணைப்புகள்</span></strong></span></span></span></span></span></p>
